---
title: Asian Beef & Roast Kumara Salad with Ginger-Soy Dressing & Peanuts
description: Mix up your salad game by incorporating a combination of textures and flavours. Hearty chunks of roasted kumara reach new levels with tender beef strips and an aromatic ginger-soy dressing, while the leafy greens and peanuts balance it all out by bringing lightness and crunch to the dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ftc-nz-asian-beef-salad-roast-kumara-850781d2.jpg
